sql:
SELECT sector, AVG(recovery_index) AS avg_recovery_index
FROM recovery_metrics
GROUP BY sector;

SELECT name, role
FROM stakeholders
WHERE stakeholder_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- Bouncing back more than the norm refers to countries with an average recovery index change above the global average;
- Typical budget for NGOs refers to the average budget allocated to NGOs within each country;
- The fastest recovering countries have the highest average recovery index change.

sql:
SELECT AVG(recovery_index_change) AS Average_Recovery_Index_Change
FROM recovery_metrics
WHERE sector = 'health' AND recovery_index_change > 5;
